OL,3,CUK Government no longer 'global
OL,4,Ccharity', aid minister to tell MPs
OL,6,FThe new aid minister will tell MPs
OL,7,Fthat the days of the British
OL,8,FGovernment acting as a "global
OL,9,Fcharity" are "over", when she faces a
OL,10,FCommons committee on Tuesday.
OL,12,FBaroness Jenny Chapman will face the
OL,13,FCommons International Development
OL,14,FCommittee for the first time since
OL,15,Ftaking the aid role in February.
