OL,3,CUK Government no longer 'global
OL,4,Ccharity', aid minister to tell MPs
OL,6,FHer appointment followed the
OL,7,Fresignation of Anneliese Dodds, who
OL,8,Fquit as development minister in
OL,9,Fprotest at the decision to cut the aid
OL,10,Fbudget to fund increased defence
OL,11,Fspending.
OL,13,FShe is expected to use her appearance
OL,14,Fbefore the committee on Tuesday to set
OL,15,Fout plans to focus aid spending on
OL,16,Fsharing British expertise, rather than
OL,17,Fproviding money, telling MPs: "The
OL,18,Fdays of viewing the UK Government as a
OL,19,Fglobal charity are over."
