OL,3,CUK Government no longer 'global
OL,4,Ccharity', aid minister to tell MPs
OL,6,FSaying the Government remains
OL,7,F"committed to international
OL,8,Fdevelopment", she will add: "We need
OL,9,Fto prioritise, be more efficient and
OL,10,Ffocus on impact above all else.
OL,12,F"We have to get the best value for
OL,13,Fmoney, for the UK taxpayer, but also
OL,14,Ffor the people we are trying to help
OL,15,Faround the world."
OL,17,FIn February the international
OL,18,Fdevelopment budget was reduced from
OL,19,F0.5% of gross national income (GNI) to
OL,20,F0.3%.
