OL,3,CUK Government no longer 'global
OL,4,Ccharity', aid minister to tell MPs
OL,6,FComing shortly after US President
OL,7,FDonald Trump's administration
OL,8,Feffectively gutted the US agency for
OL,9,Finternational development, opponents
OL,10,Fsuggested the UK cut would lead to
OL,11,Flives being lost in the developing
OL,12,Fworld.
OL,14,FBut Baroness Chapman is expected to
OL,15,Fsay that developing countries want to
OL,16,Fmove from receiving aid money to an
OL,17,Fapproach described as "partnering, not
OL,18,Fpaternalism", pointing to a deal
OL,19,Fbetween the Met Office and its
OL,20,FBangladeshi counterpart to improve
OL,21,Fflood forecasting.
